-- Switchblade --

Switchblade reaches the exit of the Pred base, then turns around to 
look at Phoenix, "Transform. I'm going to attach myself to your leg, 
then we'll get the transport vessel."

He transforms into his cyber bug-like form, and his camera regards 
Phoenix expectantly.
